The White House welcomed Gold Star Families to honor fallen heroes and their families. The statement expresses gratitude to the men and women in uniform who have made selfless sacrifices for the freedom of the American people. The nation grieves with those who have lost loved ones in service, and their sacrifices are honored. The statement also thanks those currently serving overseas and their families for their service. Prayers are sent to those in harm's way, and blessings are asked for the United States of America.